    body
        div(style='background: #f5f5f5;display: table;margin: auto;max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;')
            div(style='background: white;margin: 0;margin:20px; padding: 20px; width: 380px; max-width: 100%;')
                img(style='max-width: 130px;' src='https://testing-platinum-rail-services.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/full_logo-1582290758800.png')
                p(style="font-family:'Sf UI';") We've attached the link to assignment #{assignment.assignmentStatus}  by learner #{learner.learnerName}.
                div(style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';")
                    h4(style='margin-bottom: 2px;')
                        b Assignment Detail
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Assignment Title:   
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{assignment.assignmentTitle}
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Unit:         
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{assignment.assignmentUnit}
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Assignment:   
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{assignment.assignmentNo}
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Status:       
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{assignment.assignmentStatus}
                div(style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';")
                    h4(style='margin-bottom: 2px;')
                        b Course Details
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Title :   
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{course.courseTitle}
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Duration: 
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{course.courseDuration}
                div(style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';")
                    h4(style='margin-bottom: 2px;')
                        b Client Details
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Title :   
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{client.clientName}
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px; font-weight: 500;')
                        | Location: 
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{client.location}
